                            <comment id="54606" author="pjones" created="Thu, 21 Mar 2013 20:24:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;As per NASA ok to close ticket&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="51369" author="niu" created="Mon, 28 Jan 2013 22:07:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi, Mahmoud, if you were running quotacheck on an active system (quota was enabled before, and IO for the users with quota limit was going), these messages were expected.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The quotacheck has to disable local fs quota temporarily, which could cause dqacq/dqrel returns -EIO.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
